Package main.controllers

Class CineplexController

java.lang.Object
main.controllers.Controller
main.controllers.CineplexController
public class CineplexController extends Controller
This class manages user actions pertaining to the Cineplex and Cinema class. Stores a list of cineplexes.

  • Method Details

    • getSessions

      public static List<List<main.models.Session>> getSessions(main.models.Movie movie)
      Search all cinemas for sessions screening the given movie. Initialise a list to store lists of sessions for each cineplex. Within each cineplex sessions, sort sessions according to date, then cinema class, then time.
      Parameters:
      movie - movie to search session screenings for.
      Returns:
      List of list of sessions. Each list in the list represents sessions of a cineplex.

    • getSessions

      public static List<main.models.Session> getSessions(main.models.Cineplex cineplex)
      Search the given cineplex for all sessions in its cinemas. Sorts the sessions according to movie title, then date, then cinema class, then time.
      Parameters:
      cineplex - cineplex to search sessions for.
      Returns:
      list of sessions in the given cineplex.

    • getCineplexes

      public static List<main.models.Cineplex> getCineplexes()
      Returns:
      list of all cineplexes.

    • addSession

      public static void addSession(main.models.Cinema cinema, String movieTitle, String date, String time, boolean is3D)
      Adds a new session to the given cinema with the given fields.
      Parameters:
      cinema - cinema to add session to.
      movieTitle - title of movie that the session is screening.
      date - date of session.
      cinemaClass - class of cinema screening the session.
      time - time of session.
      is3D - if session is a 3D screening.

    • removeSession

      public static void removeSession(main.models.Cinema cinema, String movie, String date, String cinemaClass, String time)
      Removes a session with the given details from the given cinema's list of sessions.
      Parameters:
      cinema - cinema hosting the session.
      movie - movie that session is screening.
      date - date of session.
      cinemaClass - class of cinema screening the session.
      time - time of session.

    • searchSession

      public static main.models.Session searchSession(main.models.Cineplex cineplex, String movie, String date, String cinemaClass, String time)
      Searches the given cineplex for a session matching the given inputs.
      Parameters:
      cineplex - cineplex of session to search for.
      movie - movie that session is screening.
      date - date of session to search for.
      cinemaClass - class of cinema screening the session.
      time - time of session to search for.
      Returns:
      session that matches the given inputs or null if session is not found.
